ZH: 旗杆是一根支撑旗帜的竖杆。
EN: The flagpole is a vertical pole that supports the flag.

ZH: 她在旗杆上升起了国旗。
EN: She raised the national flag on the flagpole.

ZH: 旗杆上悬挂着五星红旗。
EN: The five-star red flag hangs on the flagpole.

ZH: 这座公园的旗杆非常高。
EN: The flagpole in this park is very tall.

ZH: 我站在旗杆旁，等待着队伍的到来。
EN: I stood next to the flagpole, waiting for the team to arrive.

ZH: 他们在旗杆前进行了庄严的升旗仪式。
EN: They conducted a solemn flag-raising ceremony in front of the flagpole.

ZH: 旗杆的顶部安装了一个金属球。
EN: A metal ball is installed at the top of the flagpole.

ZH: 我拍了一张旗杆上的美丽照片。
EN: I took a beautiful photo of the flagpole.

ZH: 旗杆周围有一片开满鲜花的花坛。
EN: There is a flower bed full of flowers around the flagpole.

ZH: 他抓住旗杆向上爬。
EN: He grabbed the flagpole and climbed up.

ZH: 每天清晨，他会来到旗杆前做早操。
EN: Every morning, he comes to the front of the flagpole to do morning exercises.

ZH: 孩子们用彩带装饰了旗杆，增添了节日的气氛。
EN: The children decorated the flagpole with ribbons, adding a festive atmosphere.

ZH: 风吹得旗杆摇摆不定。
EN: The wind made the flagpole sway.

ZH: 旗杆受到了严密的保护，以防止被破坏。
EN: The flagpole is being closely guarded to prevent any damage.

ZH: 我立志要攀登那座高耸的旗杆。
EN: I am determined to climb that towering flagpole.

ZH: 他把旗子绑在旗杆上。
EN: He tied the flag to the flagpole.

ZH: 旗杆上的钢丝绳需要更换了。
EN: The steel wire rope on the flagpole needs to be replaced.

ZH: 请你将旗杆擦得干净亮丽。
EN: Please clean and polish the flagpole.

ZH: 我们重新粉刷了旗杆。
EN: We repainted the flagpole.

ZH: 旗杆上镶嵌了一颗闪闪发光的红宝石。
EN: A shiny ruby is embedded on the flagpole.
